{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_08_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 粗茶ですが、どうぞ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜と遙子のユニットバトル終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After Rei and Haruko's unit battle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "病院まで付き添ってもらってすみません\nくじいた足を一通り検査してもらいましたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for making you come all the way to the hospital with me.\nI had my sprained foot examined…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6333333731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "足は捻挫も骨折もしていませんでした\n特に異常はないそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It turned out to be neither a sprain nor a fracture.\nThey said there's nothing particularly wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9333336274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 17.3204537074
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。怜がステージで転倒した時は肝を冷やしたが\n何事もなくて安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. I was really worried when you fell on stage‚  Rei‚\nbut I'm relieved that you're okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0666669607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、過労気味だから大事を取って\nしばらく安静にするように言われました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚  they told me to rest for a while\njust in case.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6771213848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "過労か……。ユニットバトルに向けて\n毎日遅くまで居残り練習をしていたようだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Overworked‚  huh…? You've been staying late every day\nto practice for the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4000014384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無理してまた倒れたりしたら大変だ。念のためしばらく\n休養して、その間のサニピの活動は四人に任せよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be bad if you overwork and collapse again. Just to be safe‚\nfully rest and leave Sunny Peace activities to the other four.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9557604154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私だけ仕事をお休みするなんて\nみんなに申し訳ないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't just take a break from work\nwhile everyone else is working. I feel bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2666681051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんにはユニットバトルの時に\n散々迷惑を掛けたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I already caused so much trouble for Haruko-san…\nduring the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0773700397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで気に病まなくていいんじゃないか？\n遙子さんだって、こんなことで怒ったりしないさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to worry about it so much.\nHaruko-san wouldn't get angry over something like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0333347718,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、遙子さんは優しいですから\n怒った顔なんて想像もつかないですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚  Haruko-san is kind‚\nso I can't even imagine her getting angry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.6000024557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2483915331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でも、ユニットバトルで\n一度だけ遙子さんが怒ったことがありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚  but Haruko-san got angry\nonce during the unit battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1000024557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8339925131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "私のせいでユニットバトルを棄権した後\n対戦相手の二人組が私をバカにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I withdrew from the unit battle because of my injury‚\nthe two members of the opposing team made fun of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.233335789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いた遙子さんが凄い剣幕で怒って\n相手の子達は圧倒されて逃げてしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san got so angry when she heard that\nand the girls were overwhelmed and ran away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6000024557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 95.9131309194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんって自分が何を言われても笑って許すのに\n仲間が悪く言われると本気で怒るんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san forgives people even when they say bad things about her‚\nbut when someone speaks ill of her friends‚  she gets seriously angry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3000024557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（いつも周囲を気遣って、自分よりも周りの人のために）\n（動いてくれる。遙子さんは昔から変わらないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's always considerate of others and acts for the sake of them）\n（rather than herself. Haruko-san hasn't changed at all since long ago.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.5000024557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 114.0751944227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それに比べて私は些細なことですぐ怒って……\nもっと遙子さんを見習わないとダメですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Compared to her‚  I get angry over the smallest things…\nI need to learn from Haruko-san more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.3666691224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 124.8251945181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに自分を卑下しなくてもいいんじゃないか？\n負けん気の強さは怜の長所でもあるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to put yourself down so much.\nBeing competitive is also one of your strengths‚  Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.233335789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3828816735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ、それで褒めてるつもりですか？\n負けん気が強いって言われても嬉しくありませんっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚  you think that's a compliment?\nI'm not happy to be called competitive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1666691224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（強がっているが、今回の件で怜も参っているようだ）\n（休養でリフレッシュ出来るといいが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's putting up a strong front‚  but Rei seems to be struggling with this incident.）\n（I hope she can refresh herself during her break.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0333286684,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.671331600009,
          "startTime": 150.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.673599943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 149.7402696615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚  good morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.7735887534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "怜？　どうしてここにいるんだ？\n今週は寮で安静にしているはずじゃなかったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei? What are you doing here?\nYou're supposed to be resting at the dorm this week‚  aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.5333093407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "そのつもりだったんですが、私の分までみんなが\n頑張ってると思うと、じっとしていられなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was‚  but I couldn't just sit around knowing that\nthey're doing their best…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.5333093407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "焦る気持ちも分かるが\n怜にとって今大事なのは体を休めることだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand you're eager.\nbut the most important thing for you now is to rest‚  Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.0999760074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……\n私、また焦ってるように見えましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh…\nDid I look impatient again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5999760074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_08_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんとも話したんです。今は焦らずに\nまずは目の前のことから一つ一つやっていこう、って",
      "translations": {
